Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.44,0:00:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock away your existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.89,0:00:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouting that you are here…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.69,0:00:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new journey begins now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.15,0:00:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As we survived through\Nthe changing seasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.10,0:00:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we gained knowledge and strength,\N(just looks like a survival game)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.65,0:00:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the forgotten memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.27,0:00:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the feelings abandoned within\Nthe flows of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have also been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.89,0:00:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When sinking down,\Nwe learned loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.31,0:00:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now we’ve met each other,\Nwe are no longer alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.90,0:01:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unveil your feelings,\NThose high emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.52,0:01:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tears will change your fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.89,0:01:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pound your heartbeat\Nagainst the darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.98,0:01:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re sure to meet,\NUnder the same flag of pain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reunion: The Remaining Time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going to happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sumaru’s mom is being\Npressed back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My star training is\Ndone my own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It shouldn’t be a match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for one who has completed\Nproper star training like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what’s with that sorry state…?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t feel even a smidgeon\Nof the power from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.56,0:02:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure enough, you’ve also got\Nside-effects from the star training…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if this life should end…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Akahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You be a good boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.27,0:03:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a simple mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll be able to come back home\Nright away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.56,0:03:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Have a safe journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:03:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sumaru…!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sumaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Akahoshi.\NWhy would you do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true then…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.89,0:05:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.48,0:05:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it was Lord Akahoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.23,0:05:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who knocked everyone out\Nand took Sumaru away?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sensei who does something\Nlike that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to students who believe in him\Nis unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why in the world…?\NWhy would you do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s all for the sake of the village…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s for the sake of taking back\Nthe star she stole!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that were the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that doesn’t make for a reason\Nto cause Sumaru pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That person is Sumaru’s mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My…mother…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, even if she is your mother,\Nshe’s now your enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person before you is\Nthe woman who stole the star
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and attempted to bring about\Nthe doom to our village!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:05:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sumaru’s mom just hid the star
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.52,0:06:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to save everyone from\Nthe pain of the training!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.89,0:06:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foolishness! Being able to die\Nfor the sake of the village
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is a Shinobi’s long-cherished dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.65,0:06:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t that right, Sumaru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re going to become the Hoshikage\Nand put to shame
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Five Great Hidden Villages\Nthat treated us with contempt, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes… I want to become the Hoshikage\Nand put them to shame…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show your foolish mother\Nyour determination!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes… I can die if it’s for\Nthe sake of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.52,0:06:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sumaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t do anything stupid, Sumaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His Chakra is in synch with Akahoshi’s.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sumaru is being controlled!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly… I have Sumaru’s life\Nin the palm of my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.48,0:06:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Natsuhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall give you the ultimate choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you take the star?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or…your son’s life?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter, Lady Natsuhi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.35,0:07:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you realized\Nyour own foolishness?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.73,0:07:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You win, Akahoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sumaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent. How did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simple, Lady Natsuhi returned it\Nwith good grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.89,0:08:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sumaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.89,0:08:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sumaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:08:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that person…really…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:08:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:09:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Multiple Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.19,0:09:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– You…! I won’t forgive you!\N– You…! I won’t forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hidden Leaf Shinobi,\NI’m your employer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– That doesn’t make any difference!\N– That doesn’t make any difference!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Neji? I can’t stand this either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.44,0:09:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! From here on is an issue\Nfor the Hidden Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s none of our concern!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That being said, are we just going\Nto leave them be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything further would be beyond\Nthe scope of the mission…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Leaf must not betray the client\Nof the accepted mission, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:10:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The star has returned.\NI’ll overlook everyone’s actions today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.94,0:10:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who wish to continue to live\Nfor the sake of the village, come with me…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But…Sumaru is…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.89,0:10:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forsake the son of the traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry. I must not leave\NSumaru behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rogue Ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.73,0:10:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hokuto! You’ll regret this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, do as you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That jerk…!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look…!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s called Natsuboshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.60,0:11:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s the other name for\Nthe planet Mars, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.98,0:11:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems it’s the same name\Nas Sumaru’s mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.48,0:11:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sumaru thinks that star\Nis protecting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Lady Natsuhi was also\Nlooking at that star.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hearts of parent and child\Nare connected!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:12:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How’re the two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.73,0:12:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re resting comfortably now…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Akahoshi attack\Nthe mother took
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when her body was weakened\Nfrom the effects of the star is a fatal one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her Chakra Network is in shreds\Nand it will mean certain death
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if she uses that Jutsu\Neven one more time…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?! But Old Lady Tsunade could…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.69,0:12:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows…?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.10,0:12:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! That Akahoshi jerk\Nis unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll kick his butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.44,0:12:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto…! You still don’t get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he’s a huge scoundrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.06,0:12:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Leaf would lose credibility
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.10,0:12:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if we do something like betraying a client.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can’t leave things be, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.15,0:12:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I also understand what\NNeji’s saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must ask the Lady Hokage\Nfor instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.81,0:12:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.81,0:12:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let’s take those two to\Nthe Village Hidden in the Leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.89,0:13:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… The Hidden Star matter\Nwill come after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sumaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re probably angry,\Naren’t you, Sumaru…?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you would resent me…\Nwho abandoned the village
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and went so far as to entrust you\Nto someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:14:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How often I attempted to take you\Nwith me…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I kept telling myself that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn’t make you happy since\NI had become a Rogue Ninja…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with this body that could\Ngive out at any time
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,due to the star training.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I often had the same dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.31,0:14:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream where I chase\Nafter you two, crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.06,0:14:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sumaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.94,0:14:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept telling myself
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that my mother was not\Na cold-hearted person
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:14:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who would leave me behind…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.27,0:15:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like that man, the Third Hoshikage said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said you had been killed by\Na Ninja from some other land,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,died and turned into a star…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said you had turned\Ninto the Natsuhiboshi…!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.69,0:15:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sumaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so…I wanted you to\Ntake me with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sumaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was lonesome… Mother…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuboshi, why are you so red?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I had a sad dream last night
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes are red, from the tears I shed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swollen as I cried…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuhiboshi, why've you lost your way?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm searching for a child\Nwho has gone afar
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.27,0:17:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't be found. though I search all day
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.15,0:17:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sad dreams come once more
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.73,0:17:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Sumaru! Wake up, Sumaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where’s the lady? Your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.15,0:18:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where’d she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.15,0:18:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it costs my life,\NI can’t let that star be…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There mustn’t be any more\Nsad mothers and children!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can’t let it happen.\Nlf she gets reckless…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and ends up using that Jutsu again…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It became the village’s power\Nand protected the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t want to have to destroy it…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But star, you have caused\Npain and suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to one too many of the children…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.73,0:19:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akahoshi…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja Art: Kujaku
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:19:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sumaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So your strength has given out?\NHow tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.48,0:20:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what’s the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.89,0:20:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn’t be! Lady Natsuhi is…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother died!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.44,0:20:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As of this moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.89,0:20:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Akahoshi, shall bear the name\Nof Fourth Hoshikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall announce the first mission\Nas Hoshikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.56,0:20:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Rogue Ninja, Sumaru and Hokuto,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Hidden Leaf Shinobi\Nare enemies who demean us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you find them attempting\Nto enter the village,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,bring them down immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.56,0:20:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.94,0:21:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.06,0:21:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will get the one who killed\Nmy mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.94,0:21:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sumaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.27,0:21:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday’s Call Sign,\Nwas all from my cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.94,0:21:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a strange park,\NI play the Fuzz Guitar without enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.89,0:21:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yellow Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.56,0:21:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, counting to three,\NI open my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.40,0:22:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Moon I am still dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.65,0:22:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at my eyes, look at my eyes,\Nas we face one another’s back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.56,0:22:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at my eyes, when can we meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EveryDay EveryNight\NWith every word I can think of
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right away, my messy feelings as is,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.73,0:22:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A magical chord change, in a restless city
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.52,0:22:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A daily JAZZ Guitar played\Nin a soft minor key
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.40,0:22:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Akahoshi jerk!\NI can’t forgive him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.27,0:22:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s diabolical.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.85,0:22:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.89,0:22:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll pound him with a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.89,0:23:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. Don’t stick your nose\Ninto their internal affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.89,0:23:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I’ll beat him into shape\Nwith my Lotus.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.56,0:23:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’d be the same as Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.19,0:23:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what’re you saying we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.65,0:23:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I’m going, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.69,0:23:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.35,0:23:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Do you guys want to start\Na war with the Hidden Star?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.23,0:23:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: “The Star’s Radiance.”
